metadata.name: XENEXIS Edition #1
metadata.description: XENEXIS is a collaborative premium membership NFT project led by an exclusive group of worldwide revolutionaries in the world of cryptocurrency. Each membership grants priority access to the project that XENEXIS has chosen through extremely selective due diligence process and allows private mint along with surprising luxury benefits. NFTs exist in 8 different types: Do, Re, Mi, Fa, Sol, La, Si, and Maestro. There are 7,888 supplies in total. Each membership has its unique traits assigned, thereby offering varying opportunities.
